In [109]:
t=0
avg=0
for i in range(0,10):
    x_train, x_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(x,y)
    cmodel.fit(x_train,y_train)
    pred = cmodel.predict_proba(x_test)
    t=log_loss(y_test,pred)
    #print(t)
    avg=avg+t
avg=avg/10
print(avg)
